Title: Sweet Caroline visits Lisbon
DateModified: '2019-02-22'
DatePublished: '2019-02-22'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/sweet-caroline-visits-lisbon
SetInCountry: Mexico
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Carolina Garza
AuthorCountry: Mexico
Text: "The story is about a girl that loves to travel and every story is situated\
  \ in a different city. The adventures of Sweet Caroline are based on real experiences\
  \ of the author which purpose is to motivate children and parents to travel, have\
  \ fun while reading and learning of real life challenges that might happen while\
  \ traveling or in the daily life. \n\nIn this story, Sweet Caroline is visiting\
  \ her cousin Charlotte which is her funniest cousin and they walk around the center\
  \ of Lisbon visiting the main attractions, enjoying local food and fado music. The\
  \ go dancing and walking aside of the river and visiting places near Lisbon."
